data.description: Location, location, location! Great move in ready horse property. Sits on 10 acres fully fenced with pipe fencing. 2 horse barns, each barn has 7 stalls, water, electric and tack room( both tack rooms can easily be converted into sleeping quarters). Each barn has 4 stalls with paddock runs and shelter. Horse shelter in one of the big paddocks, 6 horse hot walker, round pen, and exercise track. House has been fully remodeled inside. Granite counter tops and wood floors throughout. Some custom built walls, doors, island, and cabinetry. Exterior of house has been painted. Good size covered porch and huge covered patio (great for gatherings), covered side porch, outside storm shelter. Tankless water heater, 16x24 storage building/workout room (could easily be converted in to living space). Located 6 minutes from I-35, 8 minutes from Remington Park, The Zoo, Science Museum, 15 minutes from Downtown. You get the best of both worlds close to the city life and the country life! Seller is Licensed REALTOR.
